  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Validation results were obtained from bench-top experiments and reported in the evidence package; however, the structured provenance linking those results to their generating activities was not captured in the record. Decision: Accepted at Low assurance.",
